rows.label: qev087407_MSG0011
rows.name: Short on parts and short of people...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0012
rows.name:
I'd really like to get the commander's advice about how
to turn the situation around here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0001
rows.name:
Commander Vandham's a more knowledgeable
mechanic than most of the city's tech staff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0002
rows.name:
His advice saved my mechanic buddy Byron and me on
more than one occasion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0003
rows.name: The commander's an amazing man. Don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0005
rows.name:
Oh, and if you're looking for Commander Vandham,
he took off. Said you were supposed to go find him.
Something about showing you the graveyard shift?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0006
rows.name: Not sure where he is now, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087407_MSG0007
rows.name:
He was headed toward the upper administrative district,
so I figure you'll find him around there somewhere.[ST:wait ]
